main event: An object, identified as Obj 13311', was observed flying at 3,000 feet over Culebra Island, Caribbean.
interesting points: The object appeared metallic and triangular shaped., It flew level for a time before it began to descend., The observation lasted for 1 hour and 5 minutes., The object made 3 turns during its flight., An additional report indicated seeing a rocket or a similarly flying object at high speed nearby.
